<br>
2) Funseeker: one who does what s/he thinks is most fun, be it getting items or leveling, while keeping 'fun' as his primary drive.<br>
<br>
3)Casual-gamer: One who plays when times allow, not doing much to get more gaming time ( ie, an hour a day, and 2-3 weekends perhaps? )<br>
<br>
